node.text:
Gluten-free Brookie Pie
This Brookie Pie is made with a chewy, gooey almond cookie layer and baked with a fudgy brownie layer on top.

The almond cookie layer is made from whole almond ( salted or unsalted ). The cookie layer is chewy and gooey and is one of my all-time favorite Norwegian cookie dough recipes, know as kranskekake, normally baked into cookie rings. For the almond cookie dough layer, I prefer using almonds with the skin on them. It tastes so much better and gives a nice texture to the cookie crust.

The fudge brownie layer is made with both unsweetened cocoa powder and dark chocolate and has a fudgy interior and a shiny, glossy crackle top after it is baked. It is a perfect combination together with the chewy almond cookie layer. 

This Brookie Pie is quite rich; I like to chop it into bite-sized pieces, place it in a zip lock bag, place it in the freezer, and save it for a special occasion or enjoy a small piece with my coffee.

I hope you like it as much as I do.
Have a great Sunday

node.text:
Raspberry & White Vanilla Bean Cake, This white cake is what vanilla dreams are made of.

The white cake layers are soft and tender. It´s made with a vanilla-bean infused cream, The vanilla bean-infused cream turns this delightful cake into something extra-special.

After the cake layers are cooled, I fill the cake layers with homemade marshmallow fluff, kind of like a twinkie cake, which is an iconic American snack cake.

I kind of like the naked style look on this cake as seen in the photo but if you like it sweeter add more marshmallow fluff on top of the cake.

The fresh raspberries make this cake taste so fresh and balance the sweetness of the frosting and make this cake truly crave-worthy.

There is a breath of vanilla in every bite, I hope you fall in love with this white vanilla bean cake. 

#cake #twinkiecake #raspberry #summer #whitevanillacake #marshmallows #summervibes #decoration #recipes #cakerecipes #frosting #yummy #sweettooth #eeats #thefeedfeed #canon #macrophotography

node.text:
This Mocca Meringues Ice Cream cake is beyond delicious.

The cake layer is a gooey chocolate almond meringue cake.
After it is baked it is topped with a delicious Mocca ice cream, that is combined with crushed Mocca meringues.

The cake crust is gluten-free so anyone can enjoy it.
The combination of the gooey chocolate almond meringue cake, and the Mocca ice cream, combined with the crushed Mocca meringues is just something you need to make and taste to understand how delicious this ice cream cake is.

It´s the perfect ice cream cake to make in advance as it keeps well for up to two weeks in the freezer and such a crowd-pleaser. 

#glutenfree #icecream #icecreamcake #mocca #coffee #meringue #baking #recipe #favorite #macrophotography

node.text:
Using Greek Yogurt in whipped Cream makes it thick, extra creamy, and more stable than just whipped cream.

Greek Yogurt adds a subtle tanginess to the whipped cream that pairs beautifully with fresh passion fruit.

This frosting is so incredibly delicious, it´s light, creamy, thick, and the perfect summertime flavors.

You want to eat this by the spoonful it is so good!

This frosting can be used as a topping on a pavlova, as a filling inside or on the outside of your cake, or pipe onto a cupcake, or serve on the side with some strawberries or other berries.

This frosting is perfect for summer, I hope you love it as much as I do.

With Love 

#summervibes #love #yummy #sweettooth #eeats #thefeedfeed #canon #macrophotography #passionfruit #pipingtechniques  #videooftheday #whitevanillacupcake

node.text:
Vanilla Bean Flan Cake, a fluffy sponge cake layer topped with a delicious vanilla bean layer made from pastry cream, that is baked until the top of the pastry cream turns lovely brown.
Flan is one of my all-time favorites Frech pastries. The original Flan as seen in Paris is most often made with a pâte brisée sucrée bottom, I have never been a fan of that kind of bottom, In this recipe, I use a sponge cake bottom instead. 

This Flan cake is so delicious in taste and tastes even better the day after.

#flan #pastrycream #spongecake #yummy #sweettooth #love #vanilla #frenchpastrywithatwist #pink #canon #video #howtodo #eaaats

node.text:
This Scandinavia almond Coffee/Daim ice cream cake is my favorite cake/dessert. If someone asks me Manuela what is your favorite cake? This is that cake.

This ice cream cake has a gooey almonds crust, the crust is made with whipped meringues and almonds, perfect if you need to make a cake that is gluten-free.

The coffee/Daim ice cream is super simple to make and the flavors are just amazing. Even if you don't drink coffee, You are going to love this Ice Cream Cake, the coffee just gives the ice cream that little it factor.

The combination of the gooey almond crust and the coffee ice cream combined with Crushed Daim Candy is so incredibly delicious and special and perfect for any party.
 

I hope you love this ice cream as much as I do, it is so good!

#icecreamcake #myfavoritecake #daimcake #daimcandy #glutenfree #glutenfreerecipes #love #yummy #sweettooth #eats #recipe #kake #søte #canon #macrophotography

node.text:
Pillow soft and fluffy sweet buns with a creamy and dreamy custard center and juicy strawberries.

After it is baked it is drizzled with a simple glaze and coconut.

The sweet dough is made with Greek yogurt, resulting in a super soft dough, I proof the dough in the fridge overnight, or you can proof the dough for just a few hours) proofing the dough overnight makes the sweet buns just pillow-soft.

The creamy custard is the star in this recipe, it is made with real vanilla bean, heavy cream for extra richness, whole milk, sugar, cornstarch, lots of egg yolks to get this beautiful pale yellow color, and butter. After the custard is cooked, I pour the warm custard into my blender, and there is where the magic happens, there is so much richness and the vanilla flavor it is just amazing and having the custard in the blender for just a few seconds makes such a difference in texture. It is so creamy.

Adding fresh bright red strawberries ( when they are in season) into the center of the creamy custard makes for one amazing sweet bun, After the buns are baked it is drizzled with a sugar glaze and drizzles with desiccated Coconut. 

If you love sweet rolls, pastry cream, strawberries, glaze, and coconut you're going to love this one.

#custard #pastrycream #love #yummy #sweettooth #eeeeeats #scandinavianstyle #baking #recipe #love #yummy #canon #myfavorite

node.text:
Lemon Ricotta Cake, a tender and moist lemony cake bursting with lemon flavor. This cake is drizzled with warm lemon syrup right after it is baked, to make the cake even moister.

After the cake is completely cooled, I spread a generous amount of lemon curd on top and Marshmallow frosting. I then slightly toast the marshmallow Frosting in an old-fashioned way.

This Lemon Ricotta cake is tender, moist, and incredibly delicious
What is not to love! This cake is definitely one of my top 5 favorite cakes to enjoy.

#cake #lemon #ricotta #yummy #sweettooth #canon #thefeedfeed #baking #recipes

A tender white Vanilla cake frosted with marshmallow frosting, so delicious!

This white cake is made with real vanilla bean/seeds that have been steep in warm heavy cream for the ultimate vanilla flavor.

One of my favorite cakes to make and enjoy
